author: rhuijben
msg: Clean up the handling of incoming updates that change the symlinkness of a
file. After this patch incoming symlinkness changes on local-unmodified nodes
are applied, while changes on edited nodes will be marked as a tree conflict,
just like how we handle file replacements.
(file_baton): Add boolean to avoid db query.
(change_file_prop): Handle symlinkness changes before the real file/symlink
change to switch to shadowed handling as soon as possible.
(This cleanup would be required for editor v2 anyway)
(close_file): Remove the old handling that somehow also checked for local
